            , was again indicted for <rs id="t18021027-78-off430" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18021027-78-off430" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18021027-78-off430" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
