                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18021027-78-off430 t18021027-78-cd431"></join>, a pair of gold ear-rings, value 4s. and a gold pin, value 1s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18021027-78-victim694" type="victimName">
                     Sarah 
                     Ithier
                  <interp inst="t18021027-78-victim694" type="surname" value="Ithier"></interp>
